_:Nbdcb6ab0ea594a89a372792a181d6925 <http://schema.org/headLine> "PM vows to tear up “status quo” that failed young people on apprenticeships and skills" .
_:N545ee8920ba9440a8a16a9628dddaef4 <http://schema.org/itemListElement> _:N8ca6eb04ce38421abc8366e418ee87c1 .
